title: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing a highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report. Steps to reproduce: 1. Export the data in a table. Expected result: Data is successfully exported. Actual result: An exception occurs in ReportEngineService.getMetaData() function.
OB: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from a table containing a highlight/map.
EB: Data should be exported successfully when exporting from a table containing a highlight/map.
SR: 1. Open the report. 2. Export the data from the table containing the highlight/map. 3. Observe the exception that occurs in ReportEngineService.getMetaData() function.
